{"product_id":"mocha-depth","title":"MOCHA DEPTH","description":"\u003cp\u003e MALE MODEL HEIGHT 5'10 AND WAIST SIZE 32 WEARING M HOODIE.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e 420 GSM\u003cbr\u003e PREMIUM 100% COTTON FLEECE\u003cbr\u003e COMBED \u0026amp; BIO-WASHED FINISH\u003cbr\u003e YRM EMBROIDERY DETAIL ON CHEST\u003cbr\u003e EMBROIDERY DETAIL ON BACK\u003cbr\u003e SIDE YKK ZIPPER POCKETS\u003cbr\u003e KANGAROO POCKETS\u003cbr\u003e BAGGY FIT\u003cbr\u003e UNISEX ARTICLE [REFER TO SIZE CHART FOR ACCURATE MEASUREMENTS]. \u003c\/p\u003e \u003cul\u003e \u003cli\u003eUltra-heavy 420 GSM fleece delivers a rich, structured feel with lasting durability.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003cli\u003ePremium YRM embroidered chest graphic adds a bold collegiate-inspired identity.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003cli\u003eBack embroidery enhances craftsmanship and visual depth.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003cli\u003eHigh-quality YKK side zipper pockets provide secure storage with a clean silhouette.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003cli\u003eBroad, structured hood adds a relaxed yet powerful profile.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003cli\u003eFunctional kangaroo pockets offer everyday warmth and convenience.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003cli\u003eCombed and bio-washed fabric ensures softness with long-term color retention.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003cli\u003eDesigned as an elevated everyday hoodie blending luxury comfort with streetwear edge.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003c\/ul\u003e \u003ch4\u003eCare Guide\u003c\/h4\u003e \u003cul\u003e \u003cli\u003eMachine wash the hoodie inside out with like colors.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003cli\u003eUse cold water to preserve fabric quality and embroidery detail.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003cli\u003eTumble dry on low heat or air dry to prevent shrinkage.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003cli\u003eStore in a cool, dry place to maintain structure and finish.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003c\/ul\u003e \u003ch4\u003eCore Features\u003c\/h4\u003e \u003cul\u003e \u003cli\u003eHoodie constructed with 420 GSM fabric for a substantial, premium feel.\u003c\/li\u003e \u00